      "writtenOn": "2026-04-20T18:01:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "OpenSSL requires separate SSL contexts for different server certificates. We cannot present both certificates from a single context.\n\nSNI-based routing:\nSNI is already being sent by clients via our existing setCipherSuiteTLSext() function. We\u0027re using this existing protocol information to route to the appropriate context.",
